      "content": {
        "title": "Paediatric Spondylolysis and Spondylolisthesis — Core Principles",
        "definition": "Pars interarticularis defects and vertebral slippage in children and adolescents, often in athletic populations.",
        "summary": "Activity modification and bracing treat low-grade isthmic slips in adolescents. High-grade slips may require fusion in situ or reduction."
      },
      "knowledge_graph": {
